{"tid":918572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李卓人聲沙地叫香港人唔好放棄","createTime":"2018-11-27T10:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T12:06:22.000Z","uid":158074,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2fa4c8a1deaa4d10fa7b865f7877d209880239c3","tid":918572,"uid":158074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:20:07.000Z","msg":"聽到佢咁講既一刻，真係有感而發：<br />\n做人一定要夠無恥，夠面皮厚，好似D條友咁。<br />\n<br />\n先唔論佢之前既所作所為，淨講佢比人揭發袋住先，正常人都已經要即刻離開政壇搵窿捐。D條柒頭居然臉不紅咁磨爛蓆，而家仲大義懍然係度激勵香港人唔好心灰。吊那媽，李卓人唔該你收皮！"},{"pid":"7199f1f535ba86cc18e4c258707cac0fb6183277","tid":918572,"uid":120399,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母，佢輸咗之後嗰個「心淡論」真係聽到人打冷震"},{"pid":"ab713f97cabe8fa7aae42ddaf8caf1e696452243","tid":918572,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7199f1f535ba86cc18e4c258707cac0fb6183277","tid":918572,"uid":120399,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母，佢輸咗之後嗰個「心淡論」真係聽到人打冷震"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:28:55.000Z","msg":"我對香港重好熾熱，係對犯民心淡"},{"pid":"fd1a45873e32358de28bd55394961dd7d6512c0f","tid":918572,"uid":158074,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"7199f1f535ba86cc18e4c258707cac0fb6183277","tid":918572,"uid":120399,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母，佢輸咗之後嗰個「心淡論」真係聽到人打冷震"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"之前論壇佢數馮檢基如何失敗，聽完更加心寒。話晒曾經戰友，而家為個議席，咁樣數鳩對手，真係幾咁無恥。"},{"pid":"2e618ccf98ca3ceecb0ec8477829fc538495d632","tid":918572,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T10:29:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無恥 厚麵皮</blockquote><br />\n師承自港奸司徒華<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為佢地都睇通香港人<br />\n金魚記憶 + 疑中留情<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aad713d6842c41efd8fd5d734e86ea5fde488e3","tid":918572,"uid":53014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"